race.comment: The $1 million The Syndicate. PAYLINE (1) loves this distance range with three wins and a placing from five attempts and should find this a touch easier than recent Group and Listed efforts. Drawn to get a gun run in transit from gate three and his best form puts him right in this contest. GOLDEN BOOM (2) goes well for hoop Maloney who has five wins and four placings from just 12 steers. Strips fitter second-up from the break and shapes as a leading contender on best form. SPYWIRE (7) is one from one over this track and trip and should be cherry-ripe now fourth run back. In the mix. EPIC PROPORTIONS (5) was a touch plain last time out but the form prior was full of merit. Worth another chance. STORM THE RAMPARTS (6) next in line out of the astute Sydney barn.
